                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8341" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0878</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1109 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内外发力破困局：Q公司管理创新改革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internal and external efforts to break the dilemma: the road of management innovation and reform in Q company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">林春培，林倩雯，汤睿，李雅雯，纪培坤，朱晓艳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华侨大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Q公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">动力电池企业；物流配送环节；管理体制创新；革新路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Power battery enterprises, logistics and distribution links, management system innovation and innovation path</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新冠疫情的爆发使民营企业面临着内忧外患的局面，内部治理问题日益凸显，外部需求显著下降，如何突破困局成为企业首要问题。本案例描述了民营动力电池企业Q公司聘请外部专家，完善物流配送环节，改善内部治理结构，形成“理念—制度—结构—流程—技术”的革新路径。具体而言，外部专家首先全面分析企业现存的外部环境以及内部治理的困局；其次剖析问题背后的成因；再次针对相关成因为企业设置破局路径；最后联合企业高管完善内部体制设置，内外协同将路径应用于企业，成功帮助企业解决物流部门效率低下的问题。通过对以上过程的详细介绍，本案例旨在帮助学生掌握管理创新的概念、内涵和维度，引导学生了解企业实施管理创新的路径，并总结内外部联合治理对于企业管理机制改革的促进作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The outbreak of COVID-19 epidemic has made private enterprises face the situation of internal troubles and foreign invasion. The internal governance problems are increasingly prominent, and the external demand has dropped significantly. How to break through the dilemma has become the primary problem for enterprises. This case describes that Q Company, a private power battery enterprise, hired external experts, improved the logistics and distribution links, improved the internal governance structure, and formed the innovation path of &quot;idea-system-structure-process-technology&quot;. Specifically, external experts first comprehensively analyze the existing external environment of enterprises and the dilemma of internal governance; Secondly, analyze the causes behind the problem; Once again, set the breaking path for the related cause enterprises; Finally, the joint enterprise executives improved the internal system setting, and the internal and external cooperation applied the path to the enterprise, which successfully helped the enterprise solve the problem of inefficient logistics department. Through the detailed introduction of the above process, this case aims to help students master the concept, connotation and dimension of management innovation, guide students to understand the path of enterprise implementing management innovation, and summarize the promoting effect of internal and external joint governance on enterprise management mechanism reform.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理创新》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">管理创新驱动因素；管理创新结构维度；管理创新过程机制；管理创新影响因素。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
